Hello Shivam,

Thank you for contacting our support department.

For uninstalling the epp agent please use the following syntax from the windows command line :
msiexec.exe /x "path_to_msi" ADMIN_PASSWORD_0="your_uninstall_password" REBOOT=ReallySuppress REMOVE_PROP=1 /qn

Note : You will have to input your uninstall password in above command only if such a password was previously configured from server UI, otherwise you can include an empty string for field ADMIN_PASSWORD_0.

Please let us know the outcome.

Have a nice day!

Best regards,
